algorithms.centralityAlgorithms.betweenness.brandes
Class BrandesBC

java.lang.Object
  algorithms.centralityAlgorithms.betweenness.brandes.BrandesBC
All Implemented Interfaces:
BrandesBCAlgListener, CentralityAlgorithmInterface, GraphTraversalListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
TrafficMatrixBC, TrastBC, TrastLowerBoundBC, TrastUpperBoundBC
public class BrandesBC
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphTraversalListener, BrandesBCAlgListener, CentralityAlgorithmInterface

Algorithm for computing betweenness centrality as proposed by Brandes (2001). Computes betweenness INCLUDING end vertices. The class is implemented as a collection of major computation steps for easier sub-classing.
